column1: Pretty sure some meteor fragments fell around this area……
Found youuuuu! You are invited to the party, humaaan!
Huh? What the heck? Oh, it's just a fairy.
Hey, wait, don’t fly away! Come join our party!
Hinder me further, and I'll severely beat you up.
Aaa… Though it is a bit early, let’s start it now!
The party for our super busy lady!
If that's how it's gonna be…, I'm gonna beat you up and teach you a lesson, da-ze!
